Author: HoldenCaulfield7
Text: I know 6000 sounds like a lot in two days but that’s only 3000 per day so try to remember that it’s only an extra 1000 more than what maintenance would be assuming your maintenance is 2000 plus some sort of work out.   It’s not as much as you think even though in this moment it feels like it. You got this.
